    "RGBD1K contains 1050 sequences (1000 sequences for training and 50 sequences for evaluation) and more than 100 object categories, significantly enlarging both the number of sequences and object categories.",
    "The training data are sparsely annotated, with bounding boxes used for annotation of the first 600 frames for each sequence.",
    "The same attribute annotation and evaluation metrics of DepthTrack are applied.",
    "RGB-T datasetIn previous years, two RGB-T people detection datasets were used for tracking.",
    "The OTCBVS dataset [95] has six grayscale-thermal video clips captured from two outdoor scenes."
